cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.CE 

The paper deals with the simulation of diffusion-based molecular communications, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The specific application of the simulator is to model the communication process happening inside blood vessels, which is a topic related to systems biology (cs.SY) and computational biology (cs.CE). Finally, the paper presents a software platform for simulating molecular signaling, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
